snippet.title: The Foretold: Exordium GameplayTrailer
snippet.description:
Embark on an ancient Egyptian odyssey in this prequel to the gothic horror card game, The Foretold: Westmark Legacy. Build your deck, collect relics, and wield items to conquer creatures and bosses lurking in Egypt's shadows.

Game is Free to play on steam now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2432680

Developed by Nodbrim Interactive
Published by Crytivo
